               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r">fol. 1r</locus>-90v: Lectionary Readings for the Church Year, መጽሐፈ ግጻዌ፡ ኢትዮጵያዊ፡, arranged for the days of the year: e.g., Birth of Jesus (1r), Epiphany (6v), Saint Mary (13r), Martyrs (15v), Saints (17v), Angels (20v), John (the Baptist) (22v), Mount of Transfiguration (24r), Scholars (26r), The Cross (28v), Evening (28v), Palm Sunday (30r), (the wedding in) Cana of Galilee (32r), Passion Week (35v), etc. Varia: iirv: Excerpt from Gospel reading.</summary>
